{"tid":2365113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支那人戴琦：拜登優先事項包括與中國抗衡 批中國經濟不受制於民主及民意","createTime":"2021-01-13T13:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:54:13.000Z","uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43f7d7165a3f398df00990ad652dbcd486472116","tid":2365113,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"候任美國總統拜登對華態度成為各界的關注點，獲拜登提名為美國貿易代表的戴琦表示，抗衡中國的貿易行為是拜登政府上台後的政策優先事項之一。<br />\n<br />\n現年45歲的戴琦日前出席貿易業界組織的論壇，是她獲拜登提名後首度發表公開講話。她表示，拜登貿易政策的優先事項除了要確保貿易協定能夠保護及增加美國的就業機會，以協助美國勞工外，還有執行現任總統特朗普政府去年簽署的《美墨加協定》。此外，亦將會就中國的貿易行為與中國抗衡。<br />\n<br />\n戴琦續指，美國面臨着來自中國的激烈競爭，更指中國的經濟是由中國規劃部門指導，不受制於政治多元化、民主選舉、民意的壓力，稱美國將與外國盟友合作應付，而她過去曾表示過美國需強硬且有戰略地對抗中國。<br />\n<br />\n戴琦又強調，拜登尊重人權，並會推行以工人為核心的貿易政策，包括用於解決普通工人長期遭受的創傷和不滿的執行機制，令美國工人得益，更指《美墨加協定》的重要成果是納入了開創性的勞工和環境條款，而目前挑戰是要確保協議兌現承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/happening/718850/%e3%80%90%e7%be%8e%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e6%8f%90%e5%90%8d%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%be%e8%a9%b1%e3%80%91%e6%88%b4%e7%90%a6%ef%bc%9a%e6%8b%9c%e7%99%bb%e5%84%aa%e5%85%88%e4%ba%8b%e9%a0%85%e5%8c%85%e6%8b%ac%e8%88%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8a%97%e8%a1%a1-%e6%89%b9%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%97%e5%88%b6%e6%96%bc%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%b0%91%e6%84%8f/?fbclid=IwAR1Es7KSgtI-835k3cfG_9H6-Zysc-B6H_ccx77Bd255nPfeaaBEH-6mGA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fhappening%2F718850%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%25b2%25bf%25e6%2598%2593%25e4%25bb%25a3%25e8%25a1%25a8%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%2590%258d%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2594%25be%25e8%25a9%25b1%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2588%25b4%25e7%2590%25a6%25ef%25bc%259a%25e6%258b%259c%25e7%2599%25bb%25e5%2584%25aa%25e5%2585%2588%25e4%25ba%258b%25e9%25a0%2585%25e5%258c%2585%25e6%258b%25ac%25e8%2588%2587%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%258a%2597%25e8%25a1%25a1-%25e6%2589%25b9%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2588%25b6%25e6%2596%25bc%25e6%25b0%2591%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%258f%258a%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2584%258f%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Es7KSgtI-835k3cfG_9H6-Zysc-B6H_ccx77Bd255nPfeaaBEH-6mGA8&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=0a3af948\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/happening/718850/%e3%80%90%e7%be%8e%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e6%8f%90%e5%90%8d%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%be%e8%a9%b1%e3%80%91%e6%88%b4%e7%90%a6%ef%bc%9a%e6%8b%9c%e7%99%bb%e5%84%aa%e5%85%88%e4%ba%8b%e9%a0%85%e5%8c%85%e6%8b%ac%e8%88%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8a%97%e8%a1%a1-%e6%89%b9%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%97%e5%88%b6%e6%96%bc%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%b0%91%e6%84%8f/?fbclid=IwAR1Es7KSgtI-835k3cfG_9H6-Zysc-B6H_ccx77Bd255nPfeaaBEH-6mGA8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1620138165f99233fbc9c044cf86fa99c8beeeca","tid":2365113,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"獲拜登提名為美國貿易代表的戴琦表示，要求習近平主席每月將一千萬美金轉帳至拜登個人戶口是拜登政府上台後的政策優先事項之一。"},{"pid":"3fb6b9bf531f37ce1fe19b463fef3f6ddc410c6b","tid":2365113,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"戴琦幫過侵侵做野，信得過"}]}